               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Maṣḥafa taklil “Book of the Marriage Ritual” (fols. 5ra-53r) 
 -
                     Prayers on the clothes (fols. 5ra-10ra l.7) 
 - Prayers on the bride and
                     the bridegroom (fols. 10ra l.7-49v l.5) 
 - Order to be read to the bride
                     and the bridegroom (fols. 49v l.6-53r)</summary>
